<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹ymạnnạ byk tẖqtnạ fyk ntḥdy̱ byk ạlmstḥyl

[V2]
 lạ ḥd syf wlạ ạḍṭhạd hạykẖly ạ̹ymạnnạ ymyl

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̹lhnạ ạ̉qwy̱ mn kl qwẗ wkl ạ̉bwạb ạljḥym

[V4]
 tẖạbt slạmnạ rạfʿyn htạfnạ lạsm ạ̹lhnạ ạlʿẓym

[V5]
 2- lạ kẖwf yswd jwh ạlqlwb ạ̹n jznạ fy nạr ạlạ̉twn

[V6]
 ạbn ạlạ̹lh wʿdh ykwn mʿạnạ wnfwsnạ yṣwn

[V7]
 3- lmạ ạlḥyạẗ tbqy̱ fy ạ̹ydyn ạ̹lh ṣạnʿ mʿjzạt

[V8]
 wạdy ạldmwʿ hạybqy̱ ynbwʿ wyfyḍ fynạ ạltʿzyạt</lyrics>
